      "id": "899984706537066",
      "score": 1,
      "review_title": "what the hell?!",
      "review_description": "It’s honestly disappointing what happened with Lethal Ape Reborn. The game didn’t just fall short—it was outright deleted and replaced by a stupid, inferior game that completely misses what made the original worth playing in the first place.\nFans who enjoyed Lethal Ape Reborn were left with nothing, and the replacement feels lazy, uninspired, and lacking any of the charm, intensity, or fun that players originally signed up for. Instead of improving or building on what worked, it feels like everything was thrown away for something worse.\nDeleting a game people enjoyed and swapping it out for a downgrade is frustrating and disrespectful to the player base. If you were hoping for the experience Lethal Ape Reborn promised, you’re out of luck—because it’s gone, and what replaced it isn’t worth the time. 1 STAR ⭐",
      "date": 1768072632,
